he keśava | dhṛtabuddhaśarīra | dhṛtaṃ buddhasya śarīraṃ yena tasya saṃbodhanam | he dhṛtabuddhaśarīra | tvaṃ śrutijātaṃ vedārthatattvaṃ nindasi | kasya | yajñavidheḥ yajñānāṃ vidhirvidhānaṃ tasya | kiṃbhūtam | darśitapaśughātam | darśitaḥ paśughāto māraṇaṃ yena tattathā tat | athavā kiṃbhūtaṃ śrutijātam | sadayahṛdayadarśitapaśughātam | sadayahṛdayā brāhmaṇāḥ teṣāṃ darśitaḥ paśughāto māraṇaṃ yena tattathā tat | kathaṃ nindasi | ahaheti khede | gavādipaśughātaṃ dhigiti | tasya saṃbodhane | bauddhāgamaśāstre ahiṃsā paramo dharma iti nyāyāt |
